    • Method Detail

      • getResponse

        org.eclipse.emf.common.util.EList<Artifact> getResponse()
        Returns the value of the 'Response' reference list. The list contents are of type Artifact. It is bidirectional and its opposite is 'Response For'. Response artifacts passed back from the target to the source activity.
        Returns:
        the value of the 'Response' reference list.
        See Also:
        FlowPackage.getCall_Response(), Artifact.getResponseFor()

      • getResponseKeys

        org.eclipse.emf.common.util.EList<String> getResponseKeys()
        Returns the value of the 'Response Keys' attribute list. The list contents are of type String. Keys of response artifacts relative to the containing package ``artifacts/`` reference.
        Returns:
        the value of the 'Response Keys' attribute list.
        See Also:
        FlowPackage.getCall_ResponseKeys()
